This is a simple Perl script to do automatic login in MyWire portal,
a German Internet Provider.

The script needs the WWW::Mechanize from Perl.

-Instructions for Gentoo Linux:
Install the dev-perl/WWW-Mechanize ebuild.
Add the script path to /etc/conf.d/local.start

-Instructions for Ubuntu Linux:
Install the libwww-mechanize-perl package.
Add the script path to /etc/rc.local

